Given time in hours, Write a program to find the time in minute at which the minute hand and hour hand coincide in next one hour.python program

program:
current_time_hours = float(input("Enter the current time in hours: "))
minutes_per_hour = 60
minutes_per_revolution = 360 * minutes_per_hour
minutes_per_hour_hand_revolution = minutes_per_revolution / 12
minutes_per_minute_hand_revolution = minutes_per_revolution / 60
current_time_minutes = (current_time_hours * minutes_per_hour) + (current_time_hours * minutes_per_hour_hand_revolution / minutes_per_hour)
minute_hand_angle = current_time_minutes * minutes_per_minute_hand_revolution / minutes_per_hour

output:
Enter the current time in hours: 2
